; Inner passage. Leaf node of the nested fixture chain. Connects to
; the parent Entrance scope through a shot E2 -> Passage.P1 emitted
; from entrance.svx after the *include, so cavern can solve the entire
; closure as one connected component without a *fix here.
*begin Passage
*data normal from to tape compass clino
P1 P2 6.5 45 -5
P2 P3 4.0 90 0
*end Passage
